# File I/O Operations Test - ግእዝ
# Testing all file operations: read, write, append, exists, delete, list, create

ማተም "=== Testing File I/O Operations ==="

# Test 1: Write to file
ማተም "Writing to test file..."
ጻፍ "test_file.txt" "ሰላም አማርኛ! ይህ የፈተና ፋይል ነው።"

# Test 2: Check if file exists
አስተዋውቅ አለ_ነው = አለ "test_file.txt"
ማተም "File exists: " + አለ_ነው

# Test 3: Read from file
አስተዋውቅ ይዘት = አንብብ "test_file.txt"
ማተም "File content: " + ይዘት

# Test 4: Append to file
ማተም "Appending to file..."
ጨምር "test_file.txt" "\nይህ ተጨማሪ ጽሑፍ ነው።"

# Test 5: Read updated content
አስተዋውቅ አዲስ_ይዘት = አንብብ "test_file.txt"
ማተም "Updated content: " + አዲስ_ይዘት

# Test 6: Create directory
ማተም "Creating test directory..."
ፍጠር "test_directory"
አስተዋውቅ ዲሬክቶሪ_አለ = አለ "test_directory"
ማተም "Directory created: " + ዲሬክቶሪ_አለ

# Test 7: List directory contents
ማተም "Listing current directory..."
አስተዋውቅ የዲሬክቶሪ_ዝርዝር = ዝርዝር "."
ማተም "Directory contents: " + የዲሬክቶሪ_ዝርዝር

# Test 8: Write to file in subdirectory
ጻፍ "test_directory/sub_file.txt" "ይህ በዲሬክቶሪ ውስጥ ያለ ፋይል ነው።"

# Test 9: Read from subdirectory file
አስተዋውቅ የዲሬክቶሪ_ይዘት = አንብብ "test_directory/sub_file.txt"
ማተም "Subdirectory file content: " + የዲሬክቶሪ_ይዘት

# Test 10: Delete file
ማተም "Deleting test file..."
አስተዋውቅ ተሰርዟል = ሰርዝ "test_file.txt"
ማተም "File deleted: " + ተሰርዟል

# Test 11: Check if deleted file exists
አስተዋውቅ አሁን_አለ = አለ "test_file.txt"
ማተም "File still exists after deletion: " + አሁን_አለ

ማተም "\n=== All file I/O operations completed! ==="
